 Are you sure you left it here?

00:03:25.340 --> 00:03:26.180
 I must.

00:03:26.180 --> 00:03:28.180
 I've just been over at Nancy Adams's

00:03:28.180 --> 00:03:29.620
 and it isn't there any place.

00:03:29.620 --> 00:03:31.020
 Well, Henry, I don't see how you could

00:03:31.020 --> 00:03:33.100
 lose a watch on my front lawn.

00:03:33.100 --> 00:03:35.680
 This is where I remember wearing it last.

00:03:35.680 --> 00:03:38.440
 Herbert, let me see the watch you have on.

00:03:38.440 --> 00:03:40.880
 Now listen, Henry, this isn't yours.

00:03:40.880 --> 00:03:42.320
 It's exactly like mine, Herbert.

00:03:42.320 --> 00:03:43.320
 It's the same, right.

