 We're going to have clean ones.

00:08:24.740 --> 00:08:25.700
 Oh, OK.

00:08:25.700 --> 00:08:27.700
 Henry, don't break anything going through that door.

00:08:27.700 --> 00:08:28.200
 I won't.

