 Well, I guess Mary only cut four.

00:10:38.140 --> 00:10:40.140
 But I'm sure I cut five.

00:10:40.140 --> 00:10:41.260
 Well, don't go back, mother.

00:10:41.260 --> 00:10:42.300
 I can't eat a thing.

00:10:42.300 --> 00:10:43.660
 The best pie I ever ate.

