 Well, what could that be?

00:10:48.660 --> 00:10:52.300
 That whistle?

00:10:52.300 --> 00:10:53.700
 Yes.

00:10:53.700 --> 00:10:56.500
 Oh, I imagine it's just one of the fellows outside or something.

00:10:56.500 --> 00:10:58.580
 Sounded as though it would be right here in this house.

00:10:58.580 --> 00:11:00.380
 I think it was in the cellar.

00:11:00.380 --> 00:11:01.820
 From the cellar, Mary?

